DOC.brief_summary: To demonstrate the relative bioavailability of Geneva and Dista (Prozac) 20 mg Fluoxetine Hydrochloride capsules (Pulvules) in healthy adult males under fed and fasted conditions.
DOC.brief_title: To Demonstrate the Relative Bioavailability of Geneva and Dista (Prozac) 20 mg Fluoxetine Hydrochloride Capsules (Pulvules) In Healthy Adult Males Under Fed and Fasted Conditions
DOC.criteria: No clinically significant abnormal finding on physical exam, medical history, or clinical laboratory results on screening. Positive test results for HIV or hepatitis B or C. Treatment for drug or alcohol dependence.
